column5: And what do you do when there's no one that loves you?
What videogames you like to play?
You and me both. Except I'm getting really tired now. I don't have much left to give. I hope you manage it better!

Yep. I feel exactly the same. But at the age I'm at, I'm simply too tired to keep trying and I gave up on waiting for things to get better. So I'm doing my preparations, tying up lose ends etc. Hopefully it won't take long now. Best of luck to you and I hope things turn out better for you than themly did for me!
